Weinstein payed a 44 million dollar settlement and nobody saying shit, I said no one would say anything because he isn’t black there are different laws for people of color and as u can see money do not matter, cause Bill Cosby money is long too. But when you got Oprah (Weinstein’s good friend) throwing shade at MJ and u put R Kelly out there too switch narrative our people have short term memory loss, they only go hard against they own and we are the ONLY people that will throw each other under the bus it’s called “ Being on Code” all walks of life in society use this expect the majority of us.
